00071 Object *UnionClass::newObj(Database *_db) const
00072 {
00073   if (!idr_objsz)
00074     return 0;
00075 
00076   Union *t = new Union(_db);
00077 
00078   ObjectPeer::make(t, this, 0, _Union_Type, idr_objsz,
00079                       idr_psize, idr_vsize);
00080   newObjRealize(t);
00081   return t;
00082 }
